PrecisAppointment of YVON TARTE, of Masham, Quebec, as Chairperson of the Public Service Staff Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending May 6, 2001; and order that YVON TARTE shall be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act.
